Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:05.79,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121038,125792}{\fs70}Practice for "The Smile of Stone", the play that will\Ndecide the future of Tsukikage Theater, has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:09.04,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:125792,129046}Maya's role is a doll who doesn't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:14.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:129046,134092}She tries to conceptualize its movements\Nby putting bamboo sticks around her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:20.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:134092,140140}However, around that time, her mother\NHaru's condition was getting worse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.06,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141141,147064}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(800,800)}—Episode 15—\NWelcome to\NThe Underground Theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154321,156114}Look at this huge advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156114,158325}It's put on by Orion Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158325,161912}Their first day is our first day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161912,163622}It will be pretty tough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163622,166875}And where is our theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166875,168001}The basement of that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169920,171463}There?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171463,174466}We are going to play\Nin the basement of that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174466,175258}Basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175258,177761}It used to be a cafe,\Nbut it went out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180639,182265}No wonder it went out of business…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182265,184893}Don't complain.\NWe got this place for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185227,186645}Oh, it's dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186645,188689}Do you smell the dampness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188689,191274}Creepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191817,193735}The outside is pretty bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193735,195987}It's even worse inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195987,198657}I'm not sure if we can\Nmake this place pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199866,203328}Welcome to our underground theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205539,206832}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206832,209793}This is our, {\i1}our{\i0} theater here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209793,212129}That's right.\NLet's make it look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212129,214256}Let's clean it up.\NWe can make this a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214256,216800}This is our home sweet home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216800,219720}Remodeling is up to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219720,220637}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220637,221346}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221680,223390}Hey, let's get to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223390,224516}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229646,231606}Look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231606,234985}I wonder why the hell\Nthey opened up a theater there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234985,236111}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236111,238905}What happened to the fame\Nof our theater, the Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238905,241366}Well, we'll get all of the audience here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241366,242951}They'll go out of business soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242951,244202}I wonder if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247664,248957}Ms. Himekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248957,250876}I just dropped by to see the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252502,255464}You all, you shouldn't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255464,260218}But, neither Ikkakuju Theater\Nnor Tsukikage Theater is very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260218,262554}They are not even on our level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262554,263972}Besides, they are not equipped well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269144,270604}Do you know about Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270604,271354}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271354,275358}She's the girl on the truck.\NHarada Kikuko called her a "stage storm."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275358,277778}"Stage storm?"\NBy Harada Kikuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277778,279613}We can finally practice, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280280,282032}She is the stage storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282491,287496}You should be careful\Nnot to have her storm Orion Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296463,299257}Whew, we're finally done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299257,302177}Good work.\NWe have some coffee inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302177,304763}Do we have everything we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304763,308058}Yup.\NEverything is sold as is though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308058,309851}Oh?\NIt's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309851,311895}We're lucky we're done\Ncarrying everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311895,313730}Maya, come on in.\NYou'll get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316274,317317}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323532,324825}The umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331039,331832}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331832,332582}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332582,334668}Excuse me, is Sakurakōji in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334668,336211}Sakurakōji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336211,337754}Hey, that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337754,340632}Oh, the one from the donut shop…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340632,343176}…who's with different girls all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343176,344594}Sakurakōji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344594,346012}You be careful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346012,349641}He's become much of a playboy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349933,351601}Playboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351977,355564}I'm so glad Sakurakōji\Nis asking us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355772,357774}Everyone,\Neat whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357774,359192}It's all on me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359192,360694}– Really? Thank you.\N– Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360694,363572}– I'll help myself, then!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363572,364906}What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364906,366324}You'll brew it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366324,366908}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366908,369786}But your girlfriend will get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369786,370662}You have one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374916,377294}Of course you do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377294,379253}Yeah, used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379253,381798}What?\NThen, not anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381798,383675}Wow, can I put my name on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383675,385302}No!\NLet me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385302,385885}Well, why not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385885,387762}– Can we go to my birthday party?\N– Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387762,388305}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388305,390097}– I want to go, too!\N– Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:34.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390097,394728}Yeah. It's a thing of the past.\NI should put it behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403486,405947}Maya!\NMaya, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418710,420795}Why did I even run after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420795,424174}I had just decided to put all this behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424591,426927}I had so many things\NI wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426927,428887}But now it's all gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:15.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430639,435018}He's doing fine without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:18.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435018,438897}I might have just been one\Nof those many girls of his after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442817,445987}I'm here to give you your umbrella back.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445987,448239}You didn't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453995,456122}Let me walk you to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:46.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463171,466007}There are so many things\NI wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469344,470929}No words can come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473515,476059}Bye, Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476059,477310}Uhh, Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477310,478019}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478019,480981}You did great in\N"Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480981,482691}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482691,486820}But, I'm not Heathcliff,\Nunfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488321,489781}Sakurakōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:18.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492742,498581}He is as nice as he used to be,\Nbut something is different…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.75,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:500291,502751}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508633,511177}Haru, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511177,514014}I'm sorry for causing so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514014,517350}Well, we wanted to talk\Nto you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518852,520854}How about going…\Nto a rest home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524232,528486}We hate to do this,\Nbut we are in the food business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528486,531865}We cannot keep a sick person\Nin here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531865,532991}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532991,536202}You are not going to get better\Njust laying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536202,540415}Then you might as well\Nconcentrate on resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540415,545545}Maya will be very worried\Nonce she hears about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545545,550383}She is concentrating so much on acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552177,556723}The best thing for you is to get better soon,\Nand then come back and work for us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556723,560727}Before Maya gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561061,564856}Thank you so much for all\Nof your help for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564856,566066}Then, it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:33.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568693,573448}Maya, Maya…\NWhere are you and what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.66,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:577202,579662}In the basement of what used to be a cafe…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:43.24,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:579662,583249}…the practice of "The Smile of Stone"\Nheated up every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583792,587879}It's ridiculous to brush her hair everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587879,590006}How crazy is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593009,595470}I'm getting the movement\Nof a doll down little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601351,603103}This is a hard role for Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603103,605522}Yeah, she's on the stage constantly,\Nbut allowed no movement at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605522,609484}No, what I mean\Nis the time she has to sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609484,610401}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610401,612320}Just look at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614948,618743}Sakurakōji, what changed you so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:23.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619244,623706}I didn't know that it hurts so bad\Nto have someone you love leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625208,628711}Mother…\NShe must be worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628711,630505}Ever since I had left home…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.59,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630672,632590}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633883,636928}…I haven't called her even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:41.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638346,641933}No, I didn't even think about her…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641933,644769}I miss you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646229,648648}Miss Tsukikage would have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648648,649899}Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649899,653236}Are you out of your mind?\NThinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653236,655155}A doll doesn't have any emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656573,657949}Doesn't have any emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657949,661911}That's right.\NNothing in its head, nor in its heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661911,663580}That's what a doll is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669711,672380}You want to learn\Nthe emotion of a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672380,675425}Yes, I think\NI'm learning the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675425,679887}But I can't stop thinking\Nwhen I'm just sitting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683016,684809}You should go visit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684809,687187}Sansō Shrine?\NIn Saitama Prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687187,691941}Yes, go there and learn\Nhow to kill your own emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691941,693735}Kill my emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693735,697780}He can teach you\Nthe emotion of a doll there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.66,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:701201,704662}Sansō Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704996,705622}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705622,707540}Look how old it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707540,709584}I wonder what she wants me to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709584,711628}You are about to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711628,714839}Are you the ones\Nthat Miss Tsukikage sent to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714839,715715}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716633,718676}Then hurry up and come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727727,729812}He seems pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729812,732564}I wonder what relationship\Nhe has with Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732564,737111}Miss Tsukikage stayed here\Nfor a while in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737111,737862}He heard us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737862,741199}Miss Tsukikage…\NIt has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741950,744994}Okay, please get into the pose of zazen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744994,746621}Zazen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746621,750166}Yes. This is a temple of Zen.\NZen means no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750166,751751}Look what we got ourselves into.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:39.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754587,759300}Maya, did you forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759300,761469}But I haven't forgotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:44.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761469,764764}I will live until the day\NI see you again.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:55.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:775775,775775}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:59.52,0:12:59.52,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:779529,779529}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:02.44,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:782448,782448}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796212,798964}Here, straighten up your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798964,801467}It's hard to achieve emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801467,806889}There are many minds around,\Nbut look at the stone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806889,810310}There are no minds in stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810310,815064}Forget that you are a human being,\Nand become a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815064,817567}Then you will be free from your mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817567,820862}…and you will achieve\Nthe expression of emptiness on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822697,825450}Think I am a stone\Nand become… a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830204,834792}A stone doesn't think\Nabout Sakurakōji, nor about mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835293,838254}Become a stone…\NBecome a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:05.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841341,845428}Maya, it's been two years\Nsince you left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845428,847638}I bet you grew a little, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:11.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847638,851934}I have cried many times that\NI don't need you anymore, but I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:15.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851934,855396}After all, you are the only daughter I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858066,859525}Excuse me, but your magazine…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864197,866157}This is… Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866157,870119}"Natsu Eriko's acting in this play was great."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870119,874207}"But Kitajima Maya, who played\Nthe childhood Catherine, did a fantastic job…"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874207,876334}"…doing almost as well as\NNatsu's role as Catherine."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876334,879420}Maya, this is Maya.\NMy daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879420,881631}Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881631,883424}That's my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883424,888471}My daughter was in a play\Nwith Natsu Eriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888471,890223}I can't be sitting\Nlike this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890598,895686}Ladies and gentlemen,\N"The Smile of Stone" will open today at 6:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895686,899899}It starts at 6:30 PM.\NDon't miss out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.60,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:894644,897604}The Smile of Stone\NTsukikage and Ikkakuju Theaters
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901692,904153}They'll open today too, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904153,906739}Look at them.\NAlmost like touting into a cabaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906739,907865}What can they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907865,913663}We have "Hamlet" and they have\N"The Smile of Stone," which is totally unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913663,916499}Well, we'll see how many people they can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916958,920503}It starts at 6:30 PM.\NDon't miss out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920503,921753}Is it selling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921753,924382}Not at all.\NOnly four of them so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924382,926134}Four?\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926134,927718}Can I get one, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927718,929344}Yes, yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930555,931222}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934016,935560}Himekawa Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935560,937103}I am looking forward\Nto seeing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937103,938813}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940982,942567}Look how dirty it is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942567,945153}Told you we should have gone\Nto see "Hamlet."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945153,948739}What could have I done?\NIt was all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950241,953369}Everyone else here is doing the same:\Nkilling time because they couldn't get a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956873,958583}Hey, isn't that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958583,960251}…Himekawa Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962378,965423}What is Himekawa Ayumi\Ndoing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965423,968593}Hey, isn't that the guy who played\NHeathcliff in "Wuthering Heights?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968593,970970}Majima Ryo, I think his name was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:15.39,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:971804,975391}Majima Ryo had appeared to see\Nthe remembrance of Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.51,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:975391,978519}…not being able to forget\NMaya's Catherine in "Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979020,981898}Wow, we have two stars here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982482,983232}Huh, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983232,984108}It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984108,986861}No, I can't see Ms. Himekawa anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987695,991449}The plane is shaking due to turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991449,994577}Please wear your seat belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003336,1006172}{\an8}I am Prefew, an attorney.\NI heard you called for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006172,1008424}{\an8}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1007590,1010426}"The Smile of Stone"\Nhas opened its curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:54.88,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1010426,1014889}After that, the scene continued\Nwith Marisa Parsoromeo, a girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:17:00.77,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1014889,1020770}…who has lost her parents in a plane crash,\Ngiving her will to her attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023064,1026442}{\an8}Thank you for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026442,1029904}{\an8}My name is Prefew, an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026692,1027902}Where is Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031197,1033866}That's Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034367,1038037}Maya is playing a doll. Why?\NWhat's her goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038037,1041123}That's Catherine?\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041123,1043417}Ayumi?\NAyumi is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043417,1044377}Mr. Majima, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044627,1048297}…there are two wills from Marisa here.\NMay I open them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048297,1051341}Hello, everyone!\NHow do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054262,1055555}Whoa, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055555,1057974}How good looking!\NI fell in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057974,1061102}Then I will open the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063563,1065731}I, Marisa Parsoromeo…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065731,1069318}…leave all my belongings\Nto my loving doll, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073823,1075992}That's a huge doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075992,1077410}No, silly!\NThat's a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077410,1078995}Oh, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:05.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078995,1085167}Prohibited from any facial expression,\Nmovement, or words, she's not supposed to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085167,1086502}That's a hard role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086502,1089547}Catherine, where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089547,1091173}This is so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091173,1098055}My weekly salary is only 2.50 pounds,\Nand this doll is worth 65 million pounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098055,1101726}I have to brush her hair everyday like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101726,1102935}How crazy is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106772,1109899}Here, stay put.\NI have to go clean up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113404,1115740}The doll is the key to the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:40.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115740,1120870}If there's any movement that lets people know\Nthat it's a human, the play is all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120870,1125833}Miss Tsukikage sure did bet on her,\Nand she is doing fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125833,1127668}Kitajima Maya…\NWhat a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128711,1132298}This is Kitajima Maya,\Nwho wears a mask of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:56.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132298,1136636}There's no trace of the Catherine\Nwho gave me passion and kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137511,1139513}How silly was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:04.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139513,1144101}I was an actor myself, and I fell in love\Nwith Maya who wore a mask of Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147730,1150066}Good bye, my Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:22.20,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1156530,1162203}The play, which started with an audience\Nof twelve, ended in a big success.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166749,1169126}My prince Rei… I'm in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169126,1170878}I shouldn't have let her see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174465,1175716}Please, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176842,1180554}Poor people.\NThe game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180554,1182223}Poor people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184058,1187186}Yes, the people of Orion Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195444,1196862}Look at that, all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196862,1199073}That's how a theater should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202284,1205413}Hey, did you think\Nthe audience enjoyed it a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205413,1208082}Yeah, there weren't too many,\Nbut it was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208082,1210292}Those girls went crazy over Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210292,1213045}Yeah, they were like, "Mr. Rei…"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213045,1215548}No one noticed\Nthat you are a woman, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215548,1217049}Hey, watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217425,1218926}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218926,1220136}Oh, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220136,1221303}Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221595,1223055}I'm done with the backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223055,1224765}When I get you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226600,1227351}I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227351,1229477}Lord have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234775,1237236}What are you doing,\Nall smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237236,1241323}We are all here as one.\NI like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241323,1244368}That's right.\NThat's why the play went so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244368,1248956}When everyone's heart beats\Nthe same pace, there's born a great play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248956,1254462}Also, it's important for an actor to pace\Nthe heartbeat with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254462,1256130}Pace the heartbeat\Nwith the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259925,1262845}I have never thought of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262845,1265681}I only thought of acting for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:26.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282323,1286660}That's right.\NI have never thought of anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:30.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286660,1290372}I always focused on just myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:34.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290372,1294502}I just played at my own pace\Non all the other plays I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:39.67,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295878,1299673}Maya, learn how to kill your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303260,1304386}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304386,1307848}That's why Miss Tsukikage\Ngave me the role of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307848,1310267}To empty myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312561,1314313}I wonder what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314313,1317441}Seems like she's learning\Nanother step about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318442,1320402}Act to kill her own emotions…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.32,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1320402,1322321}The Smile of Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:07.78,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1324615,1327785}The word about "The Smile of Stone" spread…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:11.08,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1327785,1331080}…and the number in the audience\Ngrew as the days passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:18.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1336961,1338712}And, ten days later…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339255,1341173}Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341173,1342007}Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347429,1349139}T-This can't be…
Comment: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:50.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370369,1370369}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:03.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377669,1383799}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:09.88,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383799,1389889}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:21.89,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389889,1401899}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:34.03,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401899,1414039}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1414039,1419919}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:46.04,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419919,1426049}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:52.13,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426049,1432139}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:58.22,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432139,1438229}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:04.23,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438229,1444239}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:10.19,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1444239,1450199}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
