Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:29.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1463879,1469718}Maya thinks about her missing mother\Nand unknowingly sheds tears on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.71,0:24:35.76,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1469718,1475766}As a punishment, Miss Tsukikage\Nprohibits Maya from playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.76,0:24:40.18,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1475766,1480187}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Trace of Mother."
